wdi-BX.GSR.CMCP.ZS.def: Communications, computer, information, and other services cover international telecommunications; computer data; news-related service transactions between residents and nonresidents; construction services; royalties and license fees; miscellaneous business, professional, and technical services; personal, cultural, and recreational services; manufacturing services on physical inputs owned by others; and maintenance and repair services and government services not included elsewhere.
wdi-BX.GSR.CMCP.ZS.name: Communications, computer
wdi-BX.GSR.CMCP.ZS.source: International Monetary Fund, Balance of Payments Statistics Yearbook and data files.
